metadata.name: Gift Goat JOY (#1/555)
metadata.description:
VeeFriends Mini Drops *Gift Goat JOY* - Created By [VeeFriends](https://veefriends.com) and [JOY](https://twitter.com/johnorionyoung) *Gift Goat JOY* is a collection of 555 unique NFTs. Artist John Orion Young, known as JOY, brings his exuberant and colorful JOYWORLD style to the Gift Goat universe. The original owner of this NFT also received a June Oven, a technologically innovative space-saving smart kitchen that combines 6 appliances into one. This token is a part of the Gift Goat series and a VeeFriends Mini Drop collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain. 'Gift Goat JOY' is gift #9 of 18. This NFT does not grant you previous or future gifts from the Gift Goat Gifting Experience. For more information on the Gift Goat Series, please visit: https://veefriends.com/giftgoat JOY [joy.world](https://www.joy.world/)
